name: cathia_swashbuckler
short_description:
Hi there, welcome to the Homepage of Swashbuckler, a next generation (HTML5 based) open source business intelligence platform, which may be customized to suit the needs of your organization.
You are welcomed to visit the demo site http://swashbuckler.sourceforge.net. To receive test user account(s), please email your request to cathiabi#sina.com (change # to @). Help is wanted to translate the UI in your own language!
To know more about the project and if you know Chinese, please visit our official blog at
http://blog.sina.com.cn/cathiabi
and follow our weibo at
http://weibo.com/cathiabi
Thank you so much for reading!
summary: Next generation business intelligence platform for you
